## State Handling in UI

### Using maybeWhen (Recommended)

```dart
state.maybeWhen(
  loaded: (data) => _buildContent(data),
  error: (message) => ErrorStateWidget(message: message, onRetry: _retry),
  orElse: () => const LoadingStateWidget(),
)
```

### Using when (All states required)

```dart
state.when(
  initial: () => const SizedBox.shrink(),
  loading: () => const LoadingStateWidget(),
  loaded: (data) => _buildContent(data),
  error: (message) => ErrorStateWidget(message: message),
)
```

